k><description>&lt;p&gt;我们家委托技艺精湛的艺术家Oxcoxa绘制的全家福！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Art illustration of jam (left), their wife (right), 3 cats, and their dog - illustrated by Oxcoxa (please check out her work!)

jam has a top-knot, brown eyes, pink plastic glasses, a thick beard and mustache, septum piercing, and labret. They are wearing a orange/brown flannel with a black t-shirt underneath, black jeans and sneakers.

jam's wife has an orange beanie covering long brown hair, brown eyes, big round wireframe glasses, a septum piercing, rosy cheeks, and freckles. She is wearing a jean jacket over a black shirt, black leggings, and black boots.

jam and their wife have their arms interlocked, and the pets are around them.

Perched on jam's shoulder is the cat Soraya, a small black cat with green eyes who is looking over her shoulder, smiling and winking.

jam's wife is holding the cat Salem, a black cat with thick fur and green eyes. He is raising one paw and looks absolutely lost.

At jam's feet is the dog January, a German Shepherd/Great Pyrenees mix with brown, black, and white coloring. She is wearing a black collar and is smiling with her tongue out.

At jam's wife's feet is the cat Ellie, a round and  feisty calico with green eyes. She has her mouth open in a meow." height="2048" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jam/69ece04deb392.jpg" width="2048"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jam.some.pics"&gt;@jam&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 15:40:00 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>